content.detailedDescription: When i noticed the orb it was decending from about tree top height down to about 10 feet as it moved south. once the object got to 10 feet it turned on a spotlight scanning the ground it moved east across the property. it did not seem to notice me until it got to me. i grabbed a shotgun to shoot it out of the air as it noticed me. it shined its light on me and in a flash it was gone. it came within about 15 to 20 feet of me. it made no sound and appeared to be made of pure light. i could not make out any structure. i have no proof it happened other than my word. the property is on the corner of hoelsher lane "to the east" and virgin road " to the north". please do not list my name.
content.summary: Orb desended on west end of property then moved east across the property at about 10 feet in the he air. it looked as if it was looking for something on the ground because it had a spot light scanning the ground as it moved. it did not seem to notice me u

content.detailedDescription: My apologies as i do not remember exactly when this occurred as it was several years ago. it was between late spring and early summer of 2008. it was between 2200 and 2300 hours on a clear night. i was sitting on my back steps having a cigarette as we were living in a rental home at the time and smoking was not permitted in the house. i was with my son and his friend both of whom were 17 or 18 years of age. i was sitting on the steps facing the back yard, the boys were standing in front of me facing me and the house. it was a very quiet evening. as this was a weeknight, our neighbors were in for the night. out of the corner of my eye to my left i noticed a bright light behind my neighbors home. the home is next to mine but not attached, we shared a driveway. the light was a bright blue sphere about the size of a volleyball. it was approximately 20 feet from us.   i was at a loss for words (unusual for me)! lol. when i became quiet both boys turned to see what i was looking at. they also saw it. it was approximately 5 feet off the ground just above a fence. there was no sound. no flashing lights. just this beautiful, bright blue glowing ball floating across my neighbors yard. we kept our gaze on it, none of us speaking. we watched it slowly float across the yard towards the homes behind ours. when it reached the trees it floated up higher into the air going up and over the homes and simply disappeared from sight. no explosion of light or sound, just gone. the event only lasted a few minutes, 3 at best. when it was gone, we all continued to stare at the top of the homes where we had last seen it, wondering if it would come back. i broke the silence first saying "you both saw that, right"? both boys turned back to face me and emphatically said "oh yeah"! at this point we were all rather excited to say the least. none of us felt any fear. none of us could believe what we had just seen! we stayed out there for about another 30 minutes talking excitedly, but honestly, quite perplexed!! we were excited, confused, stunned and curious. we all agreed we had never before seen anything like it and we're all disappointed in ourselves that none of us had thought to pick up our phones and start snapping pics! we were so stunned at what we were seeing that none of us could have moved for anything. the next day at work i began searching numerous news websites to see if there had been reports of anyone else seeing this activity. i was disappointed when i found nothing. i did a search and found a site to send an inquiry to but never received a response. i do not remember the name of the organization. when i told my mother about it she said it sounded like sphere lightening. i did a search on that. i found photos of it that slightly resembled this object but nothing very close to it. once again, it was a clear night and there was no sound. i even checked online with the weather for the that night and found no inclement weather for the area on that night. i had given up on ever learning what it may have been till this evening when i was searching the channel listings and came upon your show. it renewed my interest in learning if what we saw that night has been reported by others. i thank you in advance for your time and consideration.
content.summary: Bright blue volleyball size sphere moving slowly

content.detailedDescription: Took dog out and when i looked up there was a ship hovering over the house to the south east  of the house it was there maybe a minute then it shot up into the sky and was gone..  with out a trace ... that was easter sunday morning at like 230 300 on april 12 easter sunday am i was out and came home at that time.. the next day monday april 13 was watching the show extra at like 7 pm monday evening  and there was the craft i seen on sunday morning over my house .. some one in ft meyers fl. had filmed the shop and extra had picked up the story on that ship with footage of the craft i witnessed on sunday morning at 230 300 am... i will never forget that sight ..
content.summary: Took dog out at like 3 am stood there and looked up and there it was .. then on monday 4/13 the craft was on extra that evening in ft meyers  filmed

content.detailedDescription: Sitting in the living room with the door open, about 8 pm talking to my late husband on the telephone and described to him what i saw.  it was bright and round (about the size of a truck hubcap) i was also already looking out the door.  looked like a bright light to me.  it zoomed by the open door and made a quick 95 degree turn upward and was gone.  after i finished talking to my husband called our daughter and told her. felt a little, not much, scared, but closed the door and kept watching, was happy when my husband got hom.  it zoomed off to my left and then straight up when it got to the tree line.  that's it, not much but will never forget.11
content.summary: Bright round light zoomed by the door, with a swooshing sound, made a right angle turn upwards when it got to the trees.

content.detailedDescription: We stayed in a trailer surrounded by a corn field. when i tell ppl about this particular story i tell them that me and my brother was going to the store to get kerosene. because that's what my dad did sometimes when he got off work. it only made sense to me. when reality is i don't really remember where we went. and don't remember how we got back. but we hop into the car pull down to the end of the driveway. i looked to the right and i said to him"you see that?" let's go down there. he said "hell no" and turned the other way. and it seem like when we had gotten we would of told someone but we didn't. looking back its like me and him acted as if nothing ever happened. but before that i don't know how long before we seen the stationary ufo. we had seen a ball of light fall in that corn field. don't know if it's any direct correlation. but what i did notice is how fast the military/air force, came in and bought everyone land in that area and how fast they put up a military base. as an adult my brother hates for me to bring it up in front of other friends.But he'll talk to me about it one on one. truthfully i wish i never seen it. i question everything i feel like nothing matter. besides my family of course. sometimes i question if i really seen it. and always trying to put together that whole night. and nothing comes to mind it's frustrating.
content.summary: Me and my brother was leaving we look to the right at the end of the drive way and seen this ufo hovering

content.detailedDescription: I was taking my son to school at 530 am on sept 28 2015. we were on my deck when we noticed lights in sky about 50 to 100 feet away and about 100' in the air. it stood still for a few minutes..Just hovered like tthen the lights split and started to circle each other then the lights joined and then just gone..No noise no wind just gone...It lasted about 5 minutes. no interference noticed on my cell phone or poarch light...It just took off faster than i have ever seen anything take off and no noise at all..At that height we should have heard something....
content.summary: Bright lights flew left then right lights merged then gone

content.detailedDescription:
I am a retired american airlines international captain.  i have 27,000
hours of flight time all over this planet.  i have never seen any ufo
outside of apparent satellites in the air.  but i have seen a flying
saucer !!!!!!!

in the spring of 1972 i was working as a surveyor on a huge cleared 
construction site in the goose creek area of sc.  on a morning, i and
several other work mates, were standing in the middle of the site.  i
noticed an object approaching in the sky over a tree line.  it was moving
extremely slow.  way too slow for and aircraft.  when it got within
range for me to make out the profile of the object i realized it was
a disc.  when it got to just about directly over me, i recognized that
the disc was a sky cobalt blue color on the bottom surface with a white
silhouette of a single engine aircraft of the bottom.  with no apparent
protrusions or appendages.  just a blank white silhouette. and no sound
at all.  i pointed this out to my work mates and they just laughed and
said it was a white airplane.  it was not.  it was a blue disc with
a white silhouette of a single engine aircraft on the bottom.  moving
in a straight line very slowly and with no sound.  i have spent my
entire life around aircraft.  i know what i saw and did not see.  the
disc continued to the other tree line in a straight line eventually
out of sight.  i estimate that the height was about 3 - 400 feet.

again:  i have been in the skies all over this planet but have never
seen any unexplained ufo.  but that day many years ago....I did !!!
and i have freely professed this event all my life. and i have drawn
it countless times.  it was real.  it was there.  and it was a ufo
which was obviously camouflaged as a single engine aircraft.

int captain dg aders
american airlines / retired
content.summary: Saw obvious unique camoflaged ufo

content.detailedDescription: I was turning left from us hwy 19 turning onto bonita road. it was around 4:30 pm. i was waiting to turn and looked up to see a cylinder shaped white ufo. it was longer than an airplane and had no wings or anything that looked like an airplane. it was quite a distance away and was quite big and long. i noticed the object because the cloud moved and the object was stationary. i pulled into the speedway and tried to get a picture but it was like the object just disappeared. it was no where to be found in the sky as it only took about 4-6 seconds to pull in and stop by hwy 19 at the corner.

content.detailedDescription:
I saw a round cloud bank way out in the distance around dusk. had to be around 30,000 feet in altitude. as it got darker, the object got closer to about 15,000 feet in altitude. there was a perfectly clear sky besides this cloud bank. my self and a friend went in the house and began talking at the dining room table. out of the corner of my eye  i notice flashes of light, i thought they were lighting. finally i told my friend i guess its going to start raining. i got up and went to the door, i looked out and could see what looked like a craft about 500 yards over a tree line. as the object decended behind the tree line, the white light was so bright coming between the trees. it looked like beams of white light brighter then ive ev=r seen. we watched it land, so my friend and i walked towards it. we got within 150 yards of it. it looked to have what i would call a reactor in the middle of it. this reactor looked to be vertical, cylindrical, about 96 inches around.  it was glass like you could see through it. it was swirling what looked to be like some sort of gas around this recator.
and giving off some sort of yellow, green, and red colors. over this reactor was a 40 foot dome. it seemed to be transparent. it was silent.  we got scared because we didn't know what it was. we were more scared then we had ever been before. we knew it wasnt anything from this world.  we went back to the house and got in my suburban. as we drove away it was still giving off the white light. when we got closer to it we could no longer see the white light.  we drove down a county road and saw it take off between the trees. at 3000 feet the round cloud bank appeared. it instantly went to 15,000 feet and then 30,000 feet. i mean in a nano second it was gone.
content.summary: Craft omiting bright light landed look like jellyfish or dome. looked like had a swirling glass pipe that was ae

content.detailedDescription: My friend was taking me home after school in around this time 2005. we are about a mile from my house when i see an orb in the sky. i thought i was just seeing things when we went into a small patch of woods. when we came out i looked back and now there were 3 orbs in the sky in a triangle. i told my friend to stop the car. we were across the field from my house at the time. we are now both watching these 3 orbs changing colors and moving together changing shapes, moving in patterns with each other making very fast direction changes. then they hovered in a triangle over my field and descended. i almost broke into tears. i did not want to go home at all costs. then the orbs ascended and changed forms for about another minute or so and took off with unimaginable speed. i did not want to go home afraid of what i would find but my friend reassured me that we had too. when we got back everything was normal. a few days later i checked the field for a potential landing spot and found a few laid down spots of weeds possibly deer beds. what we saw that day will affect both of us for ever. i remember the sighting like it was yesterday. this is the first time i came public with this story because i hear similar stories and hope we can figure out what actually is happening. thank you for listening.
content.flightPath: Path with directional change,Path then hovering
content.summary: 3 orb like objects changing their flight paths to creat shapes while changing colors. landed in my field about ten years ago. other witness saw the same thing. changed our lives.

content.detailedDescription: I was following my friend and ex girlfriend in my truck when they stopped in the middle of the road got out of their car and said look so i got out of my truck and there it was right over us 5 feet off the tree top all i could do is stare at it for 5 mins it was your classic ufo disk shaped with a small dome in the middle on top and 6 or 7 different color lights on the bottom and 1 bright white light in the middle. it was the size of six houses put together. after hovering for 10 mins it floated e 7 blocks and hovered above the chirch steeple and all the lights turned bright white and then it shot straight up into space instintly at light speed and it was gone. it changed my beliefs forever.
content.summary: Ufo hovered above me and my friends right above the tree top

content.detailedDescription: I am 63 now. i saw a was standing outside a store we kids used to hang out. everybody was pretty much done and i was about to go home when i noticed a ufo moving silently over a tree top mixed in clouds. i thought it was a plane it there were no sounds. i saw windows witch made me also thing it was a plane. i was dark in color and was moving in a southerly direction. i never said anything about and as for as a know, no one else did. i really didn't no what i had saw until i started watching your program.

content.detailedDescription: We were leaving family members house when noticed object following us in sky. stopped at party store to see if it would keep going. it stopped as well and hovered. when we got to our apartment building my husband went out to fields to look at it with binoculars. i went to neighbors and pounded on door. i could hear them inside but no one answered. the large light in foyer of apartment building fell to the floor breaking everywhere. no one came out it was if time was standing still. went back to apartment and object was in front of balcony. it was light bulb shaped on its side with multi colored lights. my husband finally came back inside and to this day wont discuss what happened or what he saw in the binoculars. we had many other sightings in michigan after that occurrence.
content.flightPath: Hovering then path,Path with directional change

content.detailedDescription: At approximately 130pm on october 13 2015, i was walking around my work facing north, i saw what looked like a balloon. it was a breezy day and what interested me was the consistent direction which was southwest. it flew over some clouds i would estimate to be 25 to 30 thousand feet. before i lost sight it became very bright as if the sun decided to reflect on it. prior to that there was no reflection or brightness. there were no other physical features, no wings or flashing lights. it never waivered, it was not " bouncy " or otherwise acting like a free floating balloon. it was just shaped like one and moving at a pace of a passenger airliner which i saw 10 minutes later and it looked like a plane. i didn't have much feeling about this until it became bright then i realized it was something else.
content.summary: Looked like a balloon, no physical features no wings.

content.detailedDescription: The first time i saw a ufo was in or about 1993 in saluston nc it was around 630pm me and my brother were putting shingles on a roof and he asked me to go down and start cleaning the ground and as i was picking up trash i felt a strange presence and i looked up in the sky and i saw a object hovering about a 150to 200feet going side to side up and down i was in shock standing there for about twenty minutes watching it and my brother came down and said what are you doing u didnt clean the ground and i pointed up and said look so we watched it for about another twenty minutes going up and down and side to side it didnt make a noise then my brother said lets go get out of here so we left and i was watching it through the window as he drove and i said its folliwing us so it follwed us about ten. to 15miles then it shot straight up and was gone in about a few seconds we were stunned that no one rlse had seen this then about 6 or 7 months later we saw another one this time we had more oeople around it was at my brothers house i walked around the back of his house to telieve my self and in the field i saw another onject hovering in the air about 75 feet going from side to side so i go back around the house where everyone is at and i say do you all remember that ufo me and my brother told u we saw and u all did not believe us and they said yes so i said do u want to c it because its behind the house so we all go back around the house and there it is still going sude to side f i r about twenty five minutes then it shoots straight up and is gone and this is beside a airforce base
content.summary: It was in a field with trees on both sides and it was going from side to side then shot straight up and was gone and it was beside a airforce base

content.detailedDescription: 3 witnesses in car coming off i-70 at oak grove missouri exit.  driver saw the object first and thought it was a helicopter. as it got closer no rooters or tail were seen.  the object seemed to be wobbling and the top was white and the bottom black. object was high in the sky but below the scattered cloud cover.  the driver pulled into the wallgreens parking lot where all 3 witnesses got out of the car and watched until the object disappeared in the distance. the object did not appear to reflect the sun light.  the sighting lasted about 5 minutes.  i used the compass on my phone and we were at 39deg 0' 43" n  94deg 7' 45" w.
content.summary: White dot seen high in sky. wobbling motion showing white top and black bottom.

content.detailedDescription: I was driving home bright sunny afternoon. 1 p.M. saw a silver craft hovering. almost above us. me and three kids. this is the exact day oct 13 when i saw a similar craft when i was 16 now 36. it freaked me out. i yelled to my kids to see it. they couldn't just the plane further away. i rubbed my eyes to relook and it was still there while i was driving. chrome disk. reflective. about a minute before it disappeared. rialto ca.

content.detailedDescription: While visiting mount rushmore with my family on october 13,2015, i took a variety of pictures. as i was looking at the pictures that had been photographed during our visit, i discovered what appears to be 2 circular objects over mount rushmore. i did not observe those objects while i was taking the picture. the picture was taken through my car windshield as i was driving. there was no flash from my phone. when first observed it appears to be a whispy cloud until it is enlarged. when enlarged it is appears circular, dimensional and tangible. unknown what it is or the cause.
content.summary: While reviewing pictures i took at mount rushmore, i discovered the object in a photo.

content.detailedDescription: Conditions were calm, clear, dry and sunny with few high altitude clouds. i was returning to work from lunch ~noon and heading east-bound on route 46 in parsippany, nj. a silver object roughly to my left (~10 o'clock position/northeast) caught my attention as it was low in the sky. at first i thought it was a plane but quickly noticed it had no wings or protrusions. it moved slowly but 'purposefully' in a southwesterly direction (toward me); now thinking it was a blimp by its pattern of movement. at this point (~15sec) i noticed a ring-like structure about 1/2way down the circumference that appeared to be of darker color (gunmetal gray/lead) beneath. it reminded me of a classic 1950's portrayal of a flying saucer. i thought to myself 'this must be some kind of hoax' because it was so...Perfect? the object then made a 45 degree/double-back and up turn (up and to the northeast) and vanished. it disappeared as if i unknowingly blinked my eyes...Gone! no poof of smoke, haze or fairy dust for that matter...Just gone. i looked around to other drivers and realized no one was even looking up. most people were looking down like to a cell phone/device or gazing mindlessly out the windshield at the nothingness and traffic ahead. i checked online postings but found no similar events.
content.summary: Silver round-oval object with ring gunmetal underside low altitude directional change then vanished while in clear view

content.detailedDescription: It was 2 a.M in the morning and my oldest daughter was studying for her test, and she came running to me , telling me that someone was trying to open the door and she was also hearing weird humming noises. i put the alarm on and went back to bed and she went to bed also. in the morning i took my dog to the yard at 6 in the morning and saw an imprint which is shaped like an ufo , crop  circle and it was right under the full moon. my daughter recently had a birthday party and we threw balloons out and in the morning the balloons were in a perfect line outside where the imprint was. we tried to erase the imprint but it went by itself in a n hour, i have the picture attached. my youngest daughter has always been interested in aliens and she had been trying to communicate with them.My oldest and youngest daughter have claimed to be abducted before, as they had scars on their body
content.summary: We did not see a ufo but i heard buzzing and humming and someone was trying to open the door at 2 am. there was an imprint on my window in the morning.

content.detailedDescription:
Driving from minot, nd last evening turning onto the us 52 e we observed a light that had an erratic path.  at first i thought it was a plane but there were 4 light balls that came out of it . the minute they separated they vanished but reappeared as black objects floating.  it was odd. i decided to record. it was difficult to record as the winds were strong and moving didn't help.  after about 10 min of it flying it had made it over to the far east and disappeared. 

all of a sudden nothing. at that point we arrived to velva it was dark by then so camera was not able to record - you could see the black and regular af choppers in the air and they were low.  the black choppers had no lights on them on at all times but would flash intermittently.
content.flightPath: Path with directional change,Path then hovering,Other

content.detailedDescription:
Oct 4th 2015 (maybe the night of the third)
while my wife and i were out hunting, camped at bow river cg, i was telling my her about iridium flashes. just then a bright flash occurred, se of cassiopeia. i said look there's one now. then it flashed again, brighter. we continued to watch it pulsate at various rates and intensity anywhere from 2 to 6 magnitude. the brighter flashes being the brightest object in the sky. even at its dimmest, we could still see it at an 8 magnitude. the object, over the course of an hour, made an arch type path. first following a se path then changing to an easterly path. after the change to an easterly path, it appeared that 4 other objects flew towards it and past. they were of a 7 or 8 magnitude. like satellites observed orbiting in the night sky. we watched it until it was over the ridge of the mountains. somewhere around cetus. i have observed several ufos in my life, but none like this nor for the length of time. if my wife had not seen it as well, i would have doubted my observation.
content.summary: Random-pulsating light with direction change

content.detailedDescription: I was on vacation in niagara falls canada.  i was in a crowd of people waiting for the falls to be illuminated.  it was getting dark with scattered high clouds.  i noticed the light high in the sky steadily moving from the american side of the falls to right over my head where it stopped. there were no strobe lights associated with this light.  at the same time i clearly saw a plane high in the sky and could clearly see the strobe lights and knew it was a plane.  once the light stopped moving i watched it until the clouds moved in, maybe 5 minutes.  i used the compass on my phone and it showed i was at 43deg 5' 16" n  and 79deg 4' 11" w.
content.summary: Steady moving light high in sky then stopped.

content.detailedDescription: My brother was taking video above our farm with his drone.  when he reviewed this video, a disk shaped object flies quickly by as the drone rolls to the east.  we are curious what this object could be.  it was only observed in this video.  but appears to be a disk shaped flying object.
content.summary: Observed in drone video over our farm by my brother.  file attached

content.detailedDescription:
I know this universe is big and i have always thought there is something out there but have never come close to witnessing anything. ever.

i was working out this morning at 5:15 am. not a cloud in the sky. i rarely look up but i was facing south and just looked up in the sky when i saw towards the northeast what looked like a satellite going at a normal speed and it was going southeast.  i didn't think too much about it when i saw what looked like a shooting star come from the northeast and went due south but it was going a little slower than a shooting star. i was thinking how fortunate i was to be able to see both in one night.  then 15 seconds later, 2 more things that looked like shooting stars were heading southeast at a constant rate of speed. i don't recall whether the speed changed or not but both went behind some trees and i didn't see it anymore. it was going unnaturally fast. i knew something was going on at this point and that it was not natural. i kind of got freaked out a little and called my wife to come out.  she came outside and, of course, nothing happened.  i saw one come from the southeast directly over my house and pointed but my wife didn't see it. she went back inside thinking that i'm crazy. i was thinking that myself when i saw 2 or 3 going in all different directions but on a straight line. one from the east, one from the west, one from the north. keep in mind, i am now looking straight up and i'm seeing these stars/orbs ( for lack of a better word ) moving in one direction but barely changing direction. it was not a start/stop, go backwards thing. they were just moving and gradually going in different lines when i saw one that had 3 looking stars/orbs in combined in one object and it was coming from the east and went directly over my house to the west and just disappeared after it passed me. like it disintegrated.  this really freaked me out. i ran back inside to get my wife again, who already thought i was nuts, and we stayed out there for a few more minutes. nothing was happening when i saw directly overhead a v or upside down v that looked like a geese formation. it was dark and had glowing lights under it.  it was not flashing or flickering and was moving eerily slow, but it was moving south towards tupelo.  my wife thought it was geese, which should tell you how low it was. it was definitely not geese with lights under it. i said it was 500ft high or so but it could have been only 300 ft.  i did not see anything else and in 10 minutes, the sun was starting to come up.

i know what i saw. i don't know what it was but i know what it wasn't. it was not a plane, helicopter or anything else that we know and see on a daily basis.
content.summary: I saw 3 different types of objects while working out at 5:30 am in saltillo, ms

content.detailedDescription: Driving to los alamos between 8-8.30 am on oct 13 2015 in the valle caldera (movie ranch) heading on western direction to the area of nm 4 highway in area called the chute est. height 8000 ft. witness for est. min or two min heading toward the chute area. wish the them the best of luck in their travels where ever that may be
